Come on.

00:16:21.340 --> 00:16:23.440
Instead of taking me back to the condo
to wash this off,

00:16:23.464 --> 00:16:25.480
you brought me here
to wash it with canal water?

00:16:26.018 --> 00:16:27.536
It works the same anyway.

00:16:28.146 --> 00:16:29.146
Here.

00:16:29.182 --> 00:16:31.191
We'll wipe it with alcohol
so it comes off faster.

00:16:31.458 --> 00:16:32.458
Come on.

00:16:32.541 --> 00:16:33.661
I'll help you.

00:16:34.560 --> 00:16:36.040
Hey, are there fish here?

00:16:36.579 --> 00:16:38.259
Stop being so dramatic.

00:16:48.996 --> 00:16:51.840
I'm still in shock that
you delivered a baby in the back of a car.

00:16:52.358 --> 00:16:54.758
Me too.
I didn't think I could do it.

00:16:55.668 --> 00:17:00.305
I practiced before,
but the real thing needed total focus.

00:17:01.428 --> 00:17:02.920
Two lives were in my hands.

00:17:03.826 --> 00:17:07.520
When the baby grows up, they'll have to
give you a garland on Father's Day.

00:17:08.601 --> 00:17:09.601
No need.

00:17:09.654 --> 00:17:12.980
As long as they're a good kid and
not a burden to the country, I'm happy.

00:17:14.214 --> 00:17:16.200
What? Is that a Children's day's motto?

00:17:16.636 --> 00:17:17.840
Are you the prime minister?

00:17:18.483 --> 00:17:20.360
Can I even become one? Look at me.

00:17:25.317 --> 00:17:28.593
By the way, can I ask you something?

00:17:31.293 --> 00:17:33.080
Why did you become a rescuer?

00:17:35.242 --> 00:17:36.637
I wanted to make my dad proud.

00:17:38.507 --> 00:17:39.640
I'm off to work.

00:17:40.196 --> 00:17:40.958
Alright, Dad.

00:17:41.085 --> 00:17:42.240
Can't I go with you?

00:17:42.403 --> 00:17:44.243
Stay here and take
care of your little sister.

00:17:44.602 --> 00:17:45.449
See you in the evening.

00:17:45.474 --> 00:17:46.474
Safe trip.

00:17:46.624 --> 00:17:48.032
Don't forget to come back for dinner.

00:17:48.056 --> 00:17:49.056
Okay.

00:17:55.127 --> 00:17:56.272
You're home now, Dad.

00:17:56.984 --> 00:17:58.240
You'll take care of Lew and me.

00:17:59.302 --> 00:18:01.468
Where's Mom?

00:18:02.034 --> 00:18:03.600
Mom's not coming back to us anymore.

00:18:04.650 --> 00:18:05.984
She has a new family now.

00:18:06.342 --> 00:18:09.291
But I miss Mom and Dad.

00:18:09.375 --> 00:18:11.534
It's okay. You still have me.

00:18:12.128 --> 00:18:13.200
I love you too.

00:18:14.408 --> 00:18:15.736
We'll get through this together.

00:18:33.177 --> 00:18:34.520
Your dad would be proud of you.

00:18:37.756 --> 00:18:38.756
Yours too.

00:18:40.071 --> 00:18:43.088
You're a flight attendant.
That's one of the top dream jobs.

00:18:51.515 --> 00:18:53.742
When I was a kid,
I loved sitting and watching planes.

00:18:55.539 --> 00:18:58.240
I thought if I made it there,

00:18:58.761 --> 00:19:02.173
I'd be able to escape
my dad's scolding and nagging.

00:19:03.949 --> 00:19:06.600
Up there, no one would shout.

00:19:07.604 --> 00:19:08.780
No one would judge you.

00:19:09.708 --> 00:19:11.400
That's why I wanted to go up there.

00:19:13.820 --> 00:19:16.880
Now I've made it as a flight attendant.

00:19:18.361 --> 00:19:21.200
But at the end of the day,
I'm still never good enough for my dad.

00:19:23.440 --> 00:19:25.160
There's a lot of pressure up there.

00:19:27.102 --> 00:19:29.091
I get that the sky looks
beautiful from above,

00:19:30.587 --> 00:19:32.312
but the sky down here isn't bad either.

00:19:34.018 --> 00:19:35.785
You can see the moon
reflected in the water.

00:20:21.406 --> 00:20:23.808
Hey, what are you doing?

00:20:24.761 --> 00:20:26.441
Wiping the blood off you.

00:20:27.065 --> 00:20:27.568
Oh.

00:20:27.593 --> 00:20:28.593
Come here.

00:20:30.407 --> 00:20:31.407
Turn the other way.

00:20:31.899 --> 00:20:32.899
Is there more?

00:20:33.036 --> 00:20:34.036
Hey!

00:20:34.207 --> 00:20:35.207
That got in my mouth!

00:20:35.350 --> 00:20:36.350
What's wrong with you?

00:20:36.548 --> 00:20:37.738
Here. Take that!

00:20:37.763 --> 00:20:39.518
- Take that!
- Hey, don't you know who runs this area?

00:20:39.542 --> 00:20:40.250
Take that!

00:20:40.275 --> 00:20:42.280
- Local boss, huh?
- Hey.

00:20:42.332 --> 00:20:43.536
I can drag you into the water.

00:20:43.561 --> 00:20:44.873
Don't. I'm not playing anymore.

00:20:44.898 --> 00:20:46.058
- Do you want to get in?
- No!

00:20:46.099 --> 00:20:46.895
Do you want to get your whole body in?

00:20:46.971 --> 00:20:47.680
No!

00:20:47.705 --> 00:20:48.705
I'm running away.

00:20:48.800 --> 00:20:49.800
Stop.

00:21:02.571 --> 00:21:03.800
You know how to play guitar?

00:21:04.684 --> 00:21:05.920
No, I'm practicing.

00:21:06.007 --> 00:21:07.280
Beer is teaching me.

00:21:07.727 --> 00:21:09.575
Oh, just wear that shirt for now.

00:21:09.714 --> 00:21:11.040
I'm getting yours washed.

00:21:11.310 --> 00:21:12.400
- This one?
- Yeah.

00:21:12.575 --> 00:21:13.575
What's this shirt?

00:21:13.633 --> 00:21:14.640
It's from the foundation.

00:21:15.327 --> 00:21:18.080
Wearing it makes you 50% cooler,
I'm telling you.

00:21:18.318 --> 00:21:19.680
- Seriously?
- Yeah.

00:21:20.946 --> 00:21:24.612
Then can I pass as a rescuer now?

00:21:25.296 --> 00:21:26.369
Are they still hiring?

00:21:27.315 --> 00:21:29.240
No, I wouldn't hire you.

00:21:29.994 --> 00:21:32.891
Why not? I have some skills.

00:21:33.566 --> 00:21:35.246
Why wouldn't you hire me?

00:21:40.102 --> 00:21:41.360
You're not fit to be a rescuer.

00:21:45.686 --> 00:21:47.560
You're more fit to date a rescuer.

00:22:03.184 --> 00:22:04.440
Feel free to stay here tonight.

00:22:09.581 --> 00:22:11.581
That actually sounds good.

00:22:12.675 --> 00:22:13.960
But let me make it clear.

00:22:15.085 --> 00:22:18.413
I just don't want to lie in my room
and spiral alone.

00:22:19.188 --> 00:22:20.188
Sure.

00:22:21.459 --> 00:22:23.139
But promise me one thing.

00:22:23.987 --> 00:22:24.987
What is it?

00:22:25.605 --> 00:22:26.960
Don't touch me.

00:22:28.275 --> 00:22:29.898
I don't want to be
your emotional punching bag.

00:22:29.922 --> 00:22:30.922
Please.

00:22:31.492 --> 00:22:33.040
Who would do anything to you?

00:22:34.053 --> 00:22:35.276
I'm not staying anymore.

00:22:35.728 --> 00:22:36.840
I'd better go home.

00:22:37.696 --> 00:22:38.696
Hey.

00:22:40.209 --> 00:22:41.209
What?

00:22:42.932 --> 00:22:43.960
You shouldn't be alone.

00:22:49.089 --> 00:22:50.129
Stay with me.

00:23:00.238 --> 00:23:01.238
Come on.

00:23:01.373 --> 00:23:02.440
I'll play you a song.

00:23:03.847 --> 00:23:05.743
Your ears will be
blessed, I'll have you know.

00:23:08.323 --> 00:23:09.680
Down, down,

00:23:09.736 --> 00:23:11.096
Up, up, up, down.

00:23:11.564 --> 00:23:12.388
Down,

00:23:12.444 --> 00:23:14.097
down, up, up, up,

00:23:14.122 --> 00:23:15.520
up, down.

00:23:19.036 --> 00:23:21.080
If you can't sleep, I can sing to you.

00:23:22.224 --> 00:23:24.320
Or I can tell you a
ghost story. I know a lot.

00:23:27.182 --> 00:23:29.398
Hi, Jack, The Ghost Radio.
I'm Toto.

00:23:29.625 --> 00:23:30.960
I'm calling from Samrong.

00:23:31.647 --> 00:23:33.427
I always listen live,

00:23:34.129 --> 00:23:35.615
but today I want to use protection.

00:23:39.117 --> 00:23:39.920
Hey.

00:23:40.045 --> 00:23:41.845
You're only making it
harder for me to sleep.

00:23:41.874 --> 00:23:43.680
Just you sleeping next to me is enough.

00:23:56.498 --> 00:23:57.498
Thank you

00:23:58.526 --> 00:24:00.160
for making today not so bad.

00:24:02.095 --> 00:24:03.095
Chill.

00:24:04.044 --> 00:24:05.840
I'm good at taking care of a heart.

00:24:08.204 --> 00:24:09.204
Good night.

00:24:17.734 --> 00:24:18.734
See you.

00:24:21.804 --> 00:24:22.804
In our dreams.

00:24:27.065 --> 00:24:28.114
Just sleep already.

00:24:52.269 --> 00:24:53.269
Excuse me.

00:24:53.625 --> 00:24:54.640
Can you help me?

00:24:54.776 --> 00:24:55.880
Yes, what is it?

00:24:58.906 --> 00:24:59.906
Please hurry up.

00:24:59.999 --> 00:25:01.479
I don't know how my brother is doing.

00:25:08.713 --> 00:25:09.713
Veha.

00:25:10.031 --> 00:25:11.031
Veha!

00:25:11.787 --> 00:25:12.787
Veha!

00:25:14.524 --> 00:25:15.524
Veha!

00:25:17.674 --> 00:25:18.674
Veha!

00:25:21.128 --> 00:25:22.128
Hey!

00:25:23.142 --> 00:25:24.280
What the hell are you doing?

00:25:26.756 --> 00:25:28.600
Hey! How did you get in here?

00:25:29.054 --> 00:25:30.440
Never mind how I got in.

00:25:30.530 --> 00:25:31.680
Why are you doing this?

00:25:32.020 --> 00:25:32.988
There's always tomorrow in life.

00:25:33.013 --> 00:25:34.560
You know, Toon Bodyslam's song?

00:25:34.987 --> 00:25:35.987
Huh?

00:25:36.393 --> 00:25:38.200
You're born once and you die once.

00:25:38.427 --> 00:25:40.347
Why would you waste your life
on that crappy guy?

00:25:42.077 --> 00:25:43.077
What?

00:25:43.588 --> 00:25:45.040
You think I'm committing suicide?

00:25:47.332 --> 00:25:49.440
I'm just soaking and washing myself.

00:25:50.994 --> 00:25:52.760
Oh. Really?

00:25:53.392 --> 00:25:54.392
Yes!

00:25:55.341 --> 00:25:57.808
I want to wash the bad out of myself.

00:26:00.113 --> 00:26:01.760
Can you wash off something like that?

00:26:10.479 --> 00:26:11.479
You can't.

00:26:14.032 --> 00:26:16.800
But for me, it's like starting over.

00:26:19.079 --> 00:26:22.088
I get to wash away those terrible thoughts
that made me become a side piece.

00:26:23.547 --> 00:26:27.171
Wash away all the bad feelings
I've had all this time.

00:26:31.186 --> 00:26:36.544
From now on, I'll become a new Veha
who's ready to spread his wings and fly.

00:26:38.782 --> 00:26:40.462
That's a relief to hear.

00:26:40.787 --> 00:26:43.254
You scared me. I almost gave you CPR.

00:26:46.697 --> 00:26:48.480
But why did you think I'd commit suicide?

00:26:49.327 --> 00:26:51.640
What you said the other day got me worried.

00:26:52.189 --> 00:26:54.131
I've been waiting for you
in the lobby every day.

00:26:54.858 --> 00:26:56.960
You haven't come down from your room
for days.

00:26:57.420 --> 00:26:59.100
Go ahead and insult me.

00:27:02.352 --> 00:27:03.352
I won't.

00:27:03.978 --> 00:27:05.822
I just want you to know
you're not anyone's second choice.

00:27:05.846 --> 00:27:08.680
I feel so worthless.

00:27:10.850 --> 00:27:15.184
If I weren't in the picture,
everyone would be happier, wouldn't they?

00:27:29.549 --> 00:27:30.549
Thank you.

00:27:32.879 --> 00:27:34.853
No one has ever cared about me
as much as you do.

00:27:47.814 --> 00:27:49.280
Can I join you in the tub?

00:28:01.836 --> 00:28:02.520
Hey.

00:28:02.545 --> 00:28:04.920
Are you going to take me out every day?

00:28:05.394 --> 00:28:06.108
Come on.

00:28:06.133 --> 00:28:09.871
I don't want you crying, breaking down,
or hurting yourself alone in your room.

00:28:10.006 --> 00:28:12.316
Hey. It takes time, okay?

00:28:12.517 --> 00:28:16.040
Haven't you heard of
the five stages of grief?

00:28:16.980 --> 00:28:17.793
No.

00:28:17.948 --> 00:28:18.852
The first stage is

00:28:18.902 --> 00:28:20.023
denial.

00:28:21.040 --> 00:28:22.040
Why?

00:28:22.131 --> 00:28:23.344
Why did you leave me?

00:28:23.476 --> 00:28:24.476
Why?

00:28:25.184 --> 00:28:27.893
The second stage is anger.

00:28:28.549 --> 00:28:29.800
How could you leave me?

00:28:29.880 --> 00:28:30.923
Why did you do this?

00:28:31.026 --> 00:28:32.026
Why?

00:28:32.840 --> 00:28:34.240
The third stage

00:28:34.442 --> 00:28:38.626
is bargaining.

00:28:40.210 --> 00:28:41.063
Hey.

00:28:41.130 --> 00:28:42.280
Please don't leave me.

00:28:42.717 --> 00:28:44.120
Can you come back to me?

00:28:44.726 --> 00:28:45.960
The fourth stage

00:28:46.433 --> 00:28:48.800
is depression.

00:28:51.883 --> 00:28:54.560
Why did you leave me?

00:28:59.151 --> 00:29:00.440
And the fifth stage

00:29:00.775 --> 00:29:04.640
is when you can accept the truth
and live with it.

00:29:05.376 --> 00:29:06.889
Why does it take so long to forget?

00:29:07.593 --> 00:29:09.680
Real life isn't divided
into stages like that.

00:29:12.907 --> 00:29:14.121
So what stage are you in now?

00:29:14.799 --> 00:29:17.699
Right now,
I'm entering the acceptance stage.

00:29:18.198 --> 00:29:20.720
But sometimes I still get angry
when something triggers me.

00:29:23.572 --> 00:29:26.496
But I believe that if you date me,

00:29:26.988 --> 00:29:29.840
I can get you through all those
five stages, all the way to nirvana.

00:29:32.038 --> 00:29:35.320
Date? I'm giving my heart a break.

00:29:35.592 --> 00:29:36.881
I don't care about love anymore.

00:29:37.095 --> 00:29:39.200
I want to focus on other
things in life for now.

00:29:39.744 --> 00:29:42.640
A break? You need to move on quickly.

00:29:44.221 --> 00:29:47.600
If you leave it too long,
your heart will go numb.

00:30:00.668 --> 00:30:01.749
Wanna get something to eat?

00:30:03.423 --> 00:30:04.520
Yeah, let's go.

00:30:09.736 --> 00:30:13.400
♪ Staring at the sky so wide ♪

00:30:13.704 --> 00:30:17.520
♪ Don't wanna see couples but wrong kind ♪

00:30:17.943 --> 00:30:19.961
♪ If love ain't treating you right ♪

00:30:19.986 --> 00:30:23.501
♪ If love just wastes your time ♪

00:30:25.716 --> 00:30:29.291
♪ If the one you love just don't suit ♪

00:30:29.738 --> 00:30:33.322
♪ Got nothing good for you to choose ♪

00:30:33.973 --> 00:30:35.780
♪ All you gotta do is turn around ♪

00:30:36.011 --> 00:30:39.920
♪ I'll be waiting right there ♪

00:30:40.115 --> 00:30:44.053
♪ I'm just an ordinary guy ♪
How about that?

00:30:44.148 --> 00:30:47.960
♪ Not a fancy prize, but
I'm the one they dial ♪

00:30:48.512 --> 00:30:49.512
Hey!

00:30:49.634 --> 00:30:51.057
Not bad.

00:30:54.165 --> 00:30:55.165
Whoa.

00:30:55.719 --> 00:30:56.719
Your aim is so good.

00:30:57.015 --> 00:30:58.015
I'm getting scared.

00:30:58.174 --> 00:31:00.041
Come on, don't worry.

00:31:00.066 --> 00:31:02.249
When I was aiming,
I didn't think about your face.

00:31:02.967 --> 00:31:03.967
I know.

00:31:04.499 --> 00:31:07.899
If you were thinking about me,
you'd probably use a love arrow.

00:31:09.212 --> 00:31:10.717
I can't believe you're still trying.

00:31:11.188 --> 00:31:13.280
I said I need time to heal.

00:31:14.733 --> 00:31:15.800
You focus on moving on.

00:31:17.572 --> 00:31:19.093
I'll focus on scoring points with you.

00:31:55.539 --> 00:31:57.223
Did you really bring me to a temple fair?

00:31:57.301 --> 00:31:58.526
Exactly.

00:31:59.032 --> 00:32:01.040
I brought you to see
all these people and lights,

00:32:01.486 --> 00:32:03.520
so the new Veha can shine bright.

00:32:07.668 --> 00:32:09.836
Want a doll? I'll shoot it for you.

00:32:11.639 --> 00:32:14.239
Even if I want it, I can buy it myself.

00:32:14.269 --> 00:32:17.206
Buying it isn't as valuable as
fighting for it yourself.

00:32:19.324 --> 00:32:20.960
You always try to sound cool.

00:32:24.244 --> 00:32:25.244
Of course.

00:32:25.447 --> 00:32:26.760
I have to act cool.

00:32:27.352 --> 00:32:28.914
I'm in front of a junior who's into me.

00:32:32.270 --> 00:32:36.120
I'm never going to deny you're cool.

00:32:37.348 --> 00:32:38.680
You've always been cool.

00:32:39.538 --> 00:32:42.380
But my feelings changed a long time ago.

00:32:44.445 --> 00:32:46.720
Who would be into someone for that long?

00:32:47.416 --> 00:32:48.455
There's no way.

00:32:55.309 --> 00:32:57.560
Are you sure you're not into me anymore?

00:33:07.477 --> 00:33:08.560
I want that one.

00:33:09.453 --> 00:33:10.530
Can you get it for me?

00:33:11.157 --> 00:33:12.157
Sure.

00:33:12.783 --> 00:33:15.583
Whatever doll or anything else Veha wants,

00:33:16.639 --> 00:33:18.120
Akki will get it for him.

00:33:33.576 --> 00:33:34.380
Thank you.

00:33:34.518 --> 00:33:35.518
Here.

00:33:44.089 --> 00:33:45.089
Let's go.

00:33:54.259 --> 00:33:55.259
Hey!

00:33:55.474 --> 00:33:56.682
You bumped into me too hard!

00:33:56.788 --> 00:33:59.080
Come on!
It's bumper cars. We have to bump.

00:33:59.278 --> 00:34:00.998
You're definitely getting bumped all night.

00:34:01.225 --> 00:34:03.120
You're always so dirty-minded.

00:34:03.145 --> 00:34:04.600
What are you thinking about?

00:34:04.888 --> 00:34:06.880
Your mind is getting dirty.

00:34:07.098 --> 00:34:08.800
I think you're at my level now.

00:34:24.036 --> 00:34:25.417
I've never done this before.

00:34:26.733 --> 00:34:29.480
Do you want to sit together
in the same car?

00:34:30.381 --> 00:34:31.381
Or…

00:34:31.855 --> 00:34:33.007
you can sit on my lap.

00:34:34.686 --> 00:34:36.090
The cars are so small.

00:34:36.902 --> 00:34:37.920
Let's take separate ones.

00:34:39.760 --> 00:34:41.040
Alright, I'll teach you.

00:34:41.714 --> 00:34:42.714
I'm a pro.

00:34:45.387 --> 00:34:46.387
Come on.

00:34:51.231 --> 00:34:52.351
You want some?

00:34:52.732 --> 00:34:53.350
Take that!

00:34:53.375 --> 00:34:54.375
Come on!

00:34:56.173 --> 00:34:58.213
Yeah.

00:35:03.225 --> 00:35:04.225
Oh!

00:35:04.430 --> 00:35:05.133
Hey, Ak!

00:35:05.158 --> 00:35:05.960
Hey, bro!

00:35:06.013 --> 00:35:07.040
What are you doing here?

00:35:07.411 --> 00:35:08.931
I brought Veha out.

00:35:09.187 --> 00:35:10.907
I feel bad for him. He's been feeling down.

00:35:11.186 --> 00:35:12.186
You brought Veha?

00:35:12.264 --> 00:35:13.264
Yeah.

00:35:13.599 --> 00:35:14.424
I came with Kanit.

00:35:14.502 --> 00:35:15.128
What?

00:35:15.153 --> 00:35:16.153
Yeah.

00:35:16.404 --> 00:35:17.404
Where is he?

00:35:39.559 --> 00:35:40.559
Hey!

00:35:41.913 --> 00:35:42.695
What the hell?

00:35:42.720 --> 00:35:43.920
How the hell were you driving?

00:35:44.000 --> 00:35:44.795
I'm sorry.

00:35:44.820 --> 00:35:46.400
Have you never done this before?

00:35:46.551 --> 00:35:47.178
I'm really sorry.

00:35:47.203 --> 00:35:48.880
I didn't mean it.

00:35:49.231 --> 00:35:50.494
You think an apology is going to fix this?

00:35:50.518 --> 00:35:53.840
If you want me to let it go,
pay for the damages.

00:35:54.763 --> 00:35:55.763
Are you that hurt?

00:35:55.846 --> 00:35:57.766
If it's that bad,
can I take you to the hospital?

00:35:57.797 --> 00:36:00.160
Hey. Are you trying to be a smart-ass?

00:36:00.603 --> 00:36:02.840
You hurt us. You have
to take responsibility.

00:36:03.504 --> 00:36:05.415
Please calm down.

00:36:05.443 --> 00:36:06.763
Hey! What the f*ck are you doing?

00:36:06.798 --> 00:36:07.800
Who the hell are you?

00:36:08.109 --> 00:36:09.109
I'm Toto.

00:36:11.165 --> 00:36:12.457
It's my job to take care of him.

00:36:12.524 --> 00:36:13.254
Hey!

00:36:13.304 --> 00:36:14.488
Please calm down.

00:36:14.562 --> 00:36:16.117
He was going to bump into me, not you.

00:36:16.172 --> 00:36:17.266
He meant to bump into me.

00:36:17.442 --> 00:36:18.690
I'll take responsibility.

00:36:18.837 --> 00:36:19.856
Name your price.

00:36:20.979 --> 00:36:21.979
5,000.

00:36:23.138 --> 00:36:23.880
Hey!

00:36:24.031 --> 00:36:25.031
Isn't that too much?

00:36:25.179 --> 00:36:27.640
5,000 for that small bump?
You're scammers.

00:36:27.903 --> 00:36:28.720
Don't pay them.

00:36:28.915 --> 00:36:30.480
Just apologize
and take them to the hospital.

00:36:30.504 --> 00:36:32.571
If you want money, then sue us.

00:36:32.662 --> 00:36:33.662
Okay.

00:36:34.446 --> 00:36:35.720
If I don't get money,

00:36:36.519 --> 00:36:37.520
let me punch you.

00:36:38.946 --> 00:36:40.440
How dare you hurt my bro?

00:36:40.510 --> 00:36:41.510
Asshole!

00:36:41.740 --> 00:36:42.762
Hey!

00:36:43.181 --> 00:36:44.340
What the hell do you think you're doing?

00:36:44.364 --> 00:36:45.364
Come on!

00:36:46.780 --> 00:36:47.780
Hey, stop!

00:36:50.474 --> 00:36:51.158
Bring it!

00:36:51.183 --> 00:36:52.183
Bring it!

00:36:54.060 --> 00:36:55.220
You think we can handle them?

00:36:57.166 --> 00:36:58.166
Definitely.

00:37:03.470 --> 00:37:04.308
We can definitely run!

00:37:04.333 --> 00:37:05.642
Oh, shit!

00:37:05.761 --> 00:37:06.761
Run!

00:37:09.555 --> 00:37:10.555
Hurry!

00:37:11.289 --> 00:37:12.289
Hurry!

00:37:23.272 --> 00:37:24.272
Where are they?

00:37:25.752 --> 00:37:26.840
Where did they go?

00:37:28.133 --> 00:37:29.133
Maybe that way.

00:37:29.172 --> 00:37:30.172
Let's go.

00:37:32.446 --> 00:37:34.070
Hey, they're gone.

00:37:42.205 --> 00:37:45.040
We almost got into real trouble
with the local punks.

00:37:45.867 --> 00:37:48.360
Look, I didn't want to
pick a fight with them.

00:37:48.652 --> 00:37:50.232
I was going to bump into someone else.

00:37:51.400 --> 00:37:53.440
But you couldn't bring yourself to do it,
could you?

00:37:53.817 --> 00:37:55.440
You know he feels guilty now.

00:37:59.829 --> 00:38:01.440
I think he's Lion's victim too.

00:38:04.730 --> 00:38:05.885
You're a good person.

00:38:05.979 --> 00:38:07.734
You're not capable of doing anything nasty.

00:38:08.571 --> 00:38:10.200
Leave the dirty work to me.

00:38:14.922 --> 00:38:16.860
Wanna hang out some more?
I'll take you around.

00:38:17.682 --> 00:38:18.920
I'm no longer in the mood.

00:38:19.554 --> 00:38:20.554
Let's leave.

00:38:21.900 --> 00:38:23.258
Then I'll drop you off at your condo.

00:38:23.282 --> 00:38:24.600
- Let's go.
- It's fine.

00:38:24.707 --> 00:38:26.320
I can go home by myself. You go.

00:38:26.579 --> 00:38:27.579
No.

00:38:27.701 --> 00:38:29.033
Didn't you hear what I told them?

00:38:29.624 --> 00:38:31.280
I said I'm taking care of you tonight.

00:38:36.171 --> 00:38:37.171
Let's go.

00:38:49.925 --> 00:38:51.145
Where did they go?

00:38:51.520 --> 00:38:52.545
I think that way.

00:38:52.807 --> 00:38:53.807
Come on.

00:39:01.158 --> 00:39:03.013
I thought we were going to
get beaten to death.

00:39:05.835 --> 00:39:07.000
Does it hurt a lot?

00:39:08.255 --> 00:39:09.375
Just a little.

00:39:09.862 --> 00:39:11.222
Bruises like this are no big deal.

00:39:11.786 --> 00:39:12.920
How are you feeling?

00:39:13.265 --> 00:39:14.393
Did you get hurt anywhere?

00:39:14.845 --> 00:39:15.845
I'm fine.

00:39:20.708 --> 00:39:22.490
But Kanit should've really bumped into me,

00:39:23.627 --> 00:39:27.790
so he'd be satisfied and forgive me.

00:39:34.661 --> 00:39:36.013
Stop blaming yourself.

00:39:37.298 --> 00:39:40.001
If he doesn't forgive you,
there's nothing you can do.

00:39:41.404 --> 00:39:42.680
You have to move forward.

00:39:47.988 --> 00:39:49.240
I'll stand by your side.

00:39:52.296 --> 00:39:53.296
Okay?

00:39:55.784 --> 00:39:56.784
Let's go.

00:40:09.194 --> 00:40:10.576
Be gentle.

00:40:11.331 --> 00:40:15.400
That was a close call,
fighting with those local thugs.

00:40:16.279 --> 00:40:18.107
They were the ones
who picked a fight with us.

00:40:18.252 --> 00:40:19.572
I wasn't going to let that slide.

00:40:20.354 --> 00:40:21.480
Yeah? Come here.

00:40:21.546 --> 00:40:22.586
Are you okay?

00:40:22.714 --> 00:40:23.714
Let me see.

00:40:24.294 --> 00:40:25.800
Do you have bruises anywhere?

00:40:25.998 --> 00:40:27.680
You need to look handsome for work.

00:40:28.349 --> 00:40:30.026
I'm fine.

00:40:30.219 --> 00:40:32.080
Didn't you see how fast I ran?

00:40:33.271 --> 00:40:36.171
But thank you for
making me run for my life.

00:40:37.655 --> 00:40:41.040
You like it?
I keep dragging you into random chaos.

00:40:41.978 --> 00:40:44.040
Adventure is just what I need in my life.

00:40:44.392 --> 00:40:46.360
I've been living a predictable life
for too long.

00:40:46.739 --> 00:40:50.960
Since I met you, I never know
what I'm going to face each day.

00:40:51.468 --> 00:40:52.562
It's kind of fun.

00:40:53.684 --> 00:40:56.798
I get an adrenaline rush,
all these endorphins kicking in,

00:40:58.213 --> 00:41:00.299
and I forget I'm heartbroken.

00:41:04.847 --> 00:41:05.847
That's good.

00:41:07.086 --> 00:41:09.480
Someone as cute as you
shouldn't stay sad for long.

00:41:13.097 --> 00:41:14.417
What are you talking about? Here.

00:41:14.478 --> 00:41:16.520
Whoa. You might as well punch me too.

00:41:17.333 --> 00:41:19.200
- Be gentle!
- Stay still. Let's keep this on.

00:41:19.636 --> 00:41:20.640
I can do it myself.

00:41:21.065 --> 00:41:21.878
This side too.

00:41:21.968 --> 00:41:22.968
Kanit.

00:41:26.479 --> 00:41:27.479
Lion.

00:41:33.191 --> 00:41:35.188
Where have you been?
You won't pick up my calls.

00:41:35.489 --> 00:41:37.237
I've been waiting in the lobby for a while.

00:41:38.088 --> 00:41:40.988
Why? Do I have to
report where I go to you?

00:41:41.211 --> 00:41:42.360
We're not together anymore.

00:41:44.262 --> 00:41:45.262
What's this?

00:41:45.811 --> 00:41:46.860
You broke up with me

00:41:47.193 --> 00:41:48.480
to be with this rescue guy?

00:41:49.226 --> 00:41:50.280
Isn't it too soon?

00:41:51.049 --> 00:41:53.402
Or what?
Were you secretly seeing each other

00:41:54.023 --> 00:41:55.220
while you were still with me?

00:41:56.849 --> 00:41:58.240
What if I date him?

00:41:58.566 --> 00:41:59.573
What would you do?

00:42:00.040 --> 00:42:01.040
Nothing.

00:42:01.172 --> 00:42:02.285
That'd just be fair.

00:42:02.642 --> 00:42:04.320
You messed up. I messed up.

00:42:04.931 --> 00:42:05.931
We're even.

00:42:06.706 --> 00:42:08.208
Let's go back to how we were already.

00:42:09.864 --> 00:42:12.520
Wow. Your math is shit.

00:42:14.947 --> 00:42:16.520
Let's talk nicely upstairs.

00:42:17.164 --> 00:42:19.360
You can leave now.

00:42:19.956 --> 00:42:20.946
I'm going to talk this out with him.

00:42:20.971 --> 00:42:23.720
I'm not leaving
until Kanit kicks me out himself.

00:42:23.745 --> 00:42:24.960
Then I'll pay you to leave.

00:42:25.266 --> 00:42:26.306
How much do you still owe?

00:42:26.405 --> 00:42:28.320
Just tell me the number.
I'll transfer it.

00:42:28.796 --> 00:42:29.796
From now on,

00:42:30.494 --> 00:42:31.520
stay away from him.

00:42:32.410 --> 00:42:33.480
You're ruining his image.

00:42:34.898 --> 00:42:35.898
F**k you!

00:42:36.952 --> 00:42:38.995
Hey! Why the f**k did you punch me?

00:42:39.020 --> 00:42:40.340
Because you're a f*cking asshole!

00:42:41.289 --> 00:42:42.289
Stop!

00:42:43.180 --> 00:42:44.396
Don't fight!

00:42:45.871 --> 00:42:47.280
Hey! Enough!

00:42:47.305 --> 00:42:48.305
That's enough!

00:42:49.369 --> 00:42:50.369
Bring it!

00:42:51.133 --> 00:42:52.133
Asshole!

00:42:53.865 --> 00:42:55.230
You think you're so good, huh?

00:42:55.255 --> 00:42:56.265
Son of a bitch!

00:42:56.350 --> 00:42:57.350
Enough!

00:42:58.042 --> 00:42:59.121
He punched me first!

00:42:59.146 --> 00:43:00.240
You looked down on me!

00:43:00.265 --> 00:43:00.840
Come at me!

00:43:00.912 --> 00:43:02.090
Bring it!

00:43:02.326 --> 00:43:03.766
Stop! I said stop!

00:43:04.323 --> 00:43:06.000
Look, just go.

00:43:06.299 --> 00:43:07.490
I'm staying with him tonight.

00:43:09.684 --> 00:43:11.040
Are you really getting with him?

00:43:11.146 --> 00:43:12.520
Why can't I be with him?

00:43:12.821 --> 00:43:14.021
I'm single now.

00:43:30.477 --> 00:43:31.477
Come on.

00:43:31.838 --> 00:43:33.318
Let's go to my room and keep kissing.

00:43:48.468 --> 00:43:50.280
I'm sorry for kissing you earlier.

00:43:51.298 --> 00:43:52.799
I just wanted him to leave.

00:43:54.219 --> 00:43:57.130
It's fine.
I'm definitely charging you for that.

00:43:57.995 --> 00:43:59.280
Knock it off my debt.

00:44:00.399 --> 00:44:01.151
Okay.

00:44:01.176 --> 00:44:02.950
I'll cut it down by a lot.

00:44:05.064 --> 00:44:06.125
I'm just kidding.

00:44:08.692 --> 00:44:09.692
I get you.

00:44:13.638 --> 00:44:14.640
I'm leaving now.

00:44:15.792 --> 00:44:17.400
You probably want to be alone tonight.

00:44:19.524 --> 00:44:20.720
Call me if you need anything.

00:44:30.144 --> 00:44:31.480
Can you sleep with me tonight?

00:44:35.456 --> 00:44:36.456
Sleep?

00:44:37.759 --> 00:44:40.600
You mean sleeping next to each other?

00:44:41.582 --> 00:44:42.582
Of course.

00:44:42.836 --> 00:44:43.836
Sure.

00:44:46.271 --> 00:44:47.600
I mean having sex.

00:45:00.565 --> 00:45:03.045
You're actually kind of good-looking,
the longer I look at you.

00:45:06.334 --> 00:45:07.822
I don't know how to argue with that.

00:45:09.986 --> 00:45:10.986
Then don't.

00:45:11.993 --> 00:45:13.122
Just kiss me now.

00:45:20.513 --> 00:45:21.513
No.

00:45:21.891 --> 00:45:24.251
I don't want to take advantage of
someone who's heartbroken.

00:45:25.255 --> 00:45:26.880
Why are you acting like a good guy?

00:45:29.206 --> 00:45:32.080
What's the point of being good?
Is there even a place for that?

00:45:33.594 --> 00:45:36.261
Right now, it's no morals and no limits!

00:45:36.328 --> 00:45:40.113
Hey. There are so many better people
than that thick-brow guy.

00:45:40.301 --> 00:45:41.959
Why are you taking it out on yourself
like this?

00:45:41.983 --> 00:45:43.200
You don't need to comfort me.

00:45:43.717 --> 00:45:45.757
So, what do you say?
Are you going to sleep with me?

00:45:45.849 --> 00:45:46.849
Or what?

00:45:47.070 --> 00:45:48.520
Do you want me to use these tickets?

00:45:49.180 --> 00:45:51.323
If you sleep with me tonight,

00:45:51.784 --> 00:45:53.024
- we can use all of them.
- Hey.

00:45:53.321 --> 00:45:54.321
Hey!

00:45:54.943 --> 00:45:56.760
You're acting like Lion right now.

00:46:08.615 --> 00:46:09.615
I'm sorry.

00:46:16.096 --> 00:46:17.096
Well,

00:46:17.741 --> 00:46:18.741
you can go.

00:46:20.585 --> 00:46:22.440
No one wants to stay with me anyway.

00:46:32.887 --> 00:46:34.040
If you want me to stay,

00:46:39.739 --> 00:46:40.739
I will.

00:48:05.627 --> 00:48:06.470
(Next Episode)
Debt release agreement.

00:48:06.526 --> 00:48:08.206
You don't have to take care of me anymore.

00:48:09.257 --> 00:48:10.880
Why did you bring me to our old school?

00:48:11.067 --> 00:48:12.747
To relive good memories.

00:48:12.851 --> 00:48:15.859
I'm sorry I played a part
in your bad memories.

00:48:16.312 --> 00:48:18.192
Will you give me a chance
to make things right?

00:48:21.919 --> 00:48:22.680
Hello.

00:48:22.705 --> 00:48:24.200
I came to pick Kanit up for a meal.

00:48:24.981 --> 00:48:26.200
I drive a rescue vehicle.

00:48:26.361 --> 00:48:27.881
How am I supposed to compete with him?

00:48:27.923 --> 00:48:28.960
You still have a chance.

00:48:29.077 --> 00:48:30.077
What chance?

00:48:30.197 --> 00:48:32.080
A chance to ask me out.